hopobject.body: Nice to meet you buy naturomax Tottenham spent three transfer windows chasing Brazilian midfielder Willian from two different clubs only to have Chelsea sneak in, after he’d completed a medical at White Hart Lane, and pinch his signature. With Eden Hazard, Juan Mata, Oscar, Kevin De Bruyne, Frank Lampard, Ramires, Victor Moses and others already in place at Stamford Bridge you could make a good case, as Spurs chairman Daniel Levy seems to be doing, that they did so for devilment, or to block a rival, rather than necessary squad building.
